Package: MiaoCom
Type: Package
Title: An R package for calculating comorbidity indexes for epidemiologists
Version: 0.2.3
Authors@R: person("Miao", "Cai", email = "caim29@mail.sysu.edu.cn", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Maintainer: Miao Cai <caim29@mail.sysu.edu.cn>
Description: A R package for calculating comorbidity indexes using ICD-10 coded administrative health records (i.e. Charlson Comorbidity Index, Elixhauser Comorbidity Index, and C3 Index) for epidemiologists.
